OL,6,FA local actor says his appearance in
OL,7,FBergerac is "fate" as filming for the
OL,8,Fpopular detective drama continues in
OL,9,FJersey.
OL,11,FShooting started on Thursday 22 August
OL,12,Fand will go into September with the
OL,13,FRoyal Square among the locations set
OL,14,Fto grace our screens.
OL,16,FTim Renouf, a local actor who plays a
OL,17,Fleading role in the show, tells ITV
OL,18,FChannel: "When I said 'I want to be an
OL,19,Factor', everyone from Jersey said, 'Oh
OL,20,Fwell, you know if Bergerac comes back
OL,21,Fthen you could be in that'.
