OL,6,F"It's fate I suppose. It's only when
OL,7,Fyou're actually here and you're like,
OL,8,Fthis is actually mad."
OL,10,FThe lead role of Jim Bergerac will be
OL,11,Ftaken on by Damien Molony with star
OL,12,Fnames such as Zoe Wanamaker and Philip
OL,13,FGlenister also featuring in the new
OL,14,Fseries.
