OL,6,FOn his fellow actors, Tim adds:
OL,7,F"Damien is great. Unfortunately, I
OL,8,Fdon't have any scenes with Zoe but
OL,9,Fwe're staying in the same hotel so we
OL,10,Fgot to hang out with her and her
OL,11,Fhusband last night who's an absolute
OL,12,Flegend ... and Phil Glenister who
OL,13,Fplays my dad, he's amazing."
OL,15,FLocals may recognise a few of the
OL,16,FRoyal Square market stalls as some
OL,17,Fshow off real businesses and
OL,18,Fcraftspeople.
