OL,6,FJersey artist Lauren Radley is one of
OL,7,Fthem, she explains: "It's going to be
OL,8,Ffun and good to watch.
OL,10,F"I probably shouldn't say this but
OL,11,FI've never actually seen Bergerac
OL,12,Fbefore so I'm looking forward to
OL,13,Fwatching the new series and maybe
OL,14,Fspotting myself and some other local
OL,15,Fmakers."
