OL,4,Cfilming gets underway
OL,6,FJersey has not hosted this kind of
OL,7,Ffilming in decades and although
OL,8,Ftechnology has evolved since the
OL,9,Foriginal series run in the 1980s and
OL,10,Fearly 1990s, many are glad to see it
OL,11,Freturn.
OL,13,FBrian Constantine, Executive Producer
OL,14,Fat Westward Studios, says: "It's kind
OL,15,Fof hard to believe to be honest ...
OL,16,Fit's been many years in the making,
OL,17,Fnow it's massively real and we're
OL,18,Freally humbled by how much support
OL,19,Fwe've had for the show.
