OL,6,F"It's the making of something really
OL,7,Fspecial, we're super proud and we hope
OL,8,FJersey will be too."
OL,10,FThe show will air across six episodes
OL,11,Ffor free on UKTV channel U&DRAMA and
OL,12,Fonline streaming service U in 2025.
OL,14,FLead Writer Toby Whithouse spoke
OL,15,Fexclusively to ITV News in July,
OL,16,Fsharing his hope to "keep Jersey at
OL,17,Fthe absolute heart of the show" and to
OL,18,Fbuild up the island's filming
OL,19,Finfrastructure for future series.
