OL,3,CGo behind-the-scenes on Bergerac as
OL,4,Cfilming gets underway
OL,6,FWe were invited onto set twice -
OL,7,Ffirstly at La Pulente Car Park where
OL,8,Fthey were filming in Bergerac's car,
OL,9,Fthen the Royal Square which was
OL,10,Ftransformed into a vibrant market.
OL,12,FI met Damien Molony, the new Jim
OL,13,FBergerac, on both occasions and you
OL,14,Fcould tell instantly that he had a
OL,15,Fhuge passion for the project.
OL,17,FWhen I saw him the second time, he
OL,18,Fcame straight over to us to say hello
OL,19,Fagain and remembered us from the day
OL,20,Fbefore, despite probably meeting a lot
OL,21,Fof people.
