OL,3,CGo behind-the-scenes on Bergerac as
OL,4,Cfilming gets underway
OL,6,FI spoke to him about the significance
OL,7,Fof the Royal Square, where we were,
OL,8,Fand then told him about Liberation Day.
OL,10,FIt was at this point that local actor
OL,11,FTim Renouf came over and got involved
OL,12,Fin the conversation too.
OL,14,FIt felt like everyone was very close
OL,15,Fand enjoyed working together, a good
OL,16,Fsign for the series and for showing
OL,17,Foff the island to a national audience.
